window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Six English Gentlemen with a Secret</p> <p>A Town with a Tragic Past</p> <p>And One Lunatic Sea Captain</p> <p>Letty Henderson wasn't looking for love. She was looking for more people to sell her milk and beef to. After a tragedy took the lives of her father and brother, it's all she can do to keep her little ranch running. And she wasn't the only one. The same tragedy took the lives of an entire posse, and with a town population of less than thirty, that's a lot. So is it any wonder when six English gents pass through town and offer assistance, that her head is turned in their direction? Can she stop staring at the oldest long enough to tell him what sort of help she needs? Unfortunately, the kind of help the town really needs no one can give, and even if the six men were capable of that kind of help, they weren't sticking around long enough to do any good. Or were they?</p> <p>Toss in an unlikely matchmaker and find out in this hilarious new series that delivers pure fun and romance!</p>"; 
